    "body": "Would be very nice yes.\n\nI believe this could fit in an option of the hierarchicalMenu widget, something like:\n\n``` js\nhierarchicalMenu({\n  // ... other parameters\n  breadcrumb: {\n    container: ...,\n    [template: .... (have a default template)]\n  }\n});\n```\n\nhaving a POC would be great. We then need to define what's the data sent to the template, an array would be the easiest and straightforward.\n",
