    "body": "What am I doing wrong in the code below?  Then render function is never called.\r\n\r\n```js\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.hierarchicalMenu({\r\n\tcontainer: '#Classifications',\r\n\tattributes: ['Classifications.lvl0', 'Classifications.lvl1', 'Classifications.lvl2', 'Classifications.lvl3'],\r\n\ttemplates: {\r\n\t  header: '<div style=\"font-size: medium;\">Classifications</div>',\r\n\t  item: '<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" originalAttribute=\"href\" originalPath=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"facet-item {{#isRefined}}active{{/isRefined}}\"><span class=\"facet-name\"><em class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></em> {{name}}</span class=\"facet-name\"><span>&nbsp;({{count}})</span></a>'\r\n\t},\r\n\tbreadcrumb: {\r\n\t  render: function(params) {\r\n            console.log(params.helper.getHierarchicalFacetBreadcrumb('Classifications'));\r\n            return;\r\n\t  }\r\n\t}\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
