    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@slimtimbodin Back then we decided not to implement a breadcrumb option / widget.\r\n\r\nHowever you can make a custom widget:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar search = instantsearch();\r\nsearch.addWidget({\r\n    render: function(params) {\r\n      console.log(params.helper.getHierarchicalFacetBreadcrumb('Classifications'));\r\n      // do the actual rendering here using jQuery or any library\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n```",
